BCNUDH esengi na bakonzi ba RDC kosala na lombango bolukiluki mpo na liwa lya Imam Cheikh Ali Amini o’libandela lya mposo kati na losambo azalaki kokamba.
Cheikh Ali Amini abetamaki masasi na bato bayebani te.